\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {8}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Transfer of CAD-specialised SOTA models to BenchCAD-Lite.} Both cadrille-RL and CADEvolve match published numbers on the DeepCAD test split within $\pm $0.5\,pt under our scoring infrastructure but lose 28--32\,pt on BenchCAD's standard-anchored, operation-rich evaluation. Our open BenchCAD-trained baseline (Qwen2-VL-2B SFT-only) reproduces the lineage's training stack without RL and bounds dataset difficulty with a publicly auditable lower curve.}}{17}{table.8}\protected@file@percent }
